# Sazanami Project Context

- Sazanami is a Next.js 15 Markdown corporate-site starter.
- Content lives in `content/{locale}/` and supports `ja` / `en`.
- UI messages live in `src/locales/*.json` and use `next-intl`.
- The app uses layered directories: `domain`, `application`, `infrastructure`, `presentation`, and `app`.
- Build generates `public/agent-search-index.json` for `POST /api/agent/search`.
- Agent discovery resources live at `/llms.txt`, `/SPEC.md`, and `/agent-search-index.json`.
- README files: `README.md` (English) and `README.ja.md` (Japanese).
- Use Node.js 24.
- CI targets `main`.
